{"tid":1295642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再為咗啲唔肯走嘅人留低","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T21:31:09.000Z","uid":180168,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3eba985762580641595beb950973978a95719d50","tid":1295642,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"有時要退就要快<br />\n前線實有幾個唔肯走<br />\n講咩啲咩退到幾時呀, 無退路之類嘅說話<br />\n琴日個情況跟本唔同71<br />\n無時間畀你地討論呀 勸人走<br />\n<br />\n同埋好老實講<br />\n你地走晒得返幾個人<br />\n佢地自然會退㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n琴日捉咗嗰幾個<br />\n唔方會係堅持要留低嘅人<br />\n希望各位反省<br />\n同埋了解be water真締"},{"pid":"bbc5d11ed34edbeff0b335da35afdb22438294e6","tid":1295642,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:42:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推上熱門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，光復行動冇可能每日都做<br />\n好似屯門公園搞到今日咁烏煙瘴氣區議員責無旁貸<br />\n要清洗屯門公園始終要由根源做起<br />\n所以除左投立法會外<br />\n都請記得投票區議會踢走自動當選建制派<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾建制派霸哂啲議席<br />\n就算唔係參選都可以做提名人，義工，助選團<br />\n行出第一步拒絕自動當選！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=8de90ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n登記左做選民既全部入group<br />\n急需大量提名人，義工助選團，Design等職位<br />\n入group後右下角Discuss入公頻搵各區admin<br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警濫權一定要有議員抗衡<br />\n否則只會一直任人魚肉"},{"pid":"b292797191edf57831ea234ba45972a7840c0ace","tid":1295642,"uid":258441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"e0017e8ccfd844f5ab23b2086a8afc04e257237e","tid":1295642,"uid":240534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"光復運動應該停止！唔好俾人帶風向！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfmeFT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfmeFT</a>"},{"pid":"5088e094ab92d119253d2c95567e8d69bd46996d","tid":1295642,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d30235d5828b82795ee4c3ccef9b3c3e253b00","tid":1295642,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推畀所有人睇"},{"pid":"92678855e38ecd61cc1e0ac801a7cbac83b0f0a9","tid":1295642,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}